pageContext.description: Winged Axe No stop ridge, but thickening near end of wings. Edge fairly sharp. Butt thin.
pageContext.other: Weight given as 14 ozs (approx). I have converted to grams but I put 400 rather than 397 as 397 suggests it is more accurate than "approx." implies. FYI: The word "flanged" in "flanged axe" has been corrected twice on this card - in the heading it has been replaced with "half-flanged", but in the Description it has been replaced with "winged".
